data.description: LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATION! END UNIT! RARE OPPORTUNITY! Discover the perfect blend of convenience and comfort in desirable Chelsea Commons. This super charming cottage-style townhouse is close to shopping, restaurants, schools, and churches, offering unparalleled accessibility to all your daily amenities. This residence is a quiet end unit, providing a truly serene retreat. Enjoy the ease of single-story living, eliminating the need for stairs to access your bedrooms. The exterior boasts a charming pea gravel and large stepping stone walkway, leading to a private backyard oasis. Inside, the light and bright home welcomes you with 9-foot ceilings throughout, creating an airy and spacious atmosphere. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room and dining room, providing an ideal setting for entertaining and relaxation. Cozy up to the traditional wood-burning fireplace in the living room, adding warmth and character to the space. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring a gas slide-in range and a large pantry for ample storage. The generous primary bedroom offers a comfortable retreat, while the main bathroom features a shower-only design for convenience. The property shines with an inviting sunroom that leads to a private patio area, perfect for enjoying sunny afternoons or quiet evenings outdoors. The community exudes a nice feel and is exceptionally people and pet-friendly, creating a welcoming and inclusive atmosphere. Don't miss the chance to call this gem your home, where every detail has been thoughtfully considered to offer a delightful living experience. Embrace the best of both convenience and comfort in this inviting property. Schedule your tour today!
